This spec ies has passed for a long time under the name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1831" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="427" pageNumber="428" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dentellum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="427" pageNumber="428">Bembidion dentellum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Thunberg, 1787).
</paragraph>
